'''Kamō no Kus''' (蒲生のクス, かもうのクス) is a giant [[:en:Camphora officinarum|kusunoki]] tree located within the precincts of {{ill|Kamō Hachiman Shrine|ja|蒲生八幡神社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kamō Hachiman Shrine|qq=}} in Kamō Town, upper Hisayutaka, in [[:en:Aira, Kagoshima|Aira City]], [[:en:Kagoshima Prefecture|Kagoshima Prefecture]]. It has been designated as a National {{ill|Special Natural Monument|ja|特別天然記念物|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Special Natural Monument|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 天然記念物|comment=enwiki is a redirect|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 天然記念物|comment=enwiki is a redirect}}.

== Overview ==
{{Location map+|Japan Kagoshima Prefecture|relief=1|width=240|float=right|caption=Location of {{ill|Kamō no Kus|ja|蒲生のクス|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kamō no Kus|qq=}}|places=
